an item is eliminated, please contact us for a revised&nbsp;quote.&nbsp;<br=
>
<br>
The starting price on our website and sample label is based on large quanti=
ties of the most cost-effective size, color, and finish of a product delive=
red to a nearby port for import items. If your&nbsp;quote&nbsp;is for small=
er quantities it could have significantly
 higher pricing as it will not qualify for volume discounts and&nbsp;may be=
 subject to small order fees, split&nbsp;pallet fees, and other surcharges&=
nbsp;levied at the factory level.&nbsp;<br>
