Lead times are estimated and are contingent on stock levels and production =
schedules at the time of order.&nbsp;If the material is in stock at the tim=
e of order please add 2 to 5 days for processing and packing.&nbsp;<strong>=
For tile requiring production, l</strong><strong>ead
 time is calculated as Production + Transit time. For example, an item requ=
iring 4-6 weeks production and 5-7 weeks transit would result in a total es=
timated lead time of 9-13 weeks.&nbsp;</strong>We may be able to narrow dow=
n the lead time at the time of order.
 Please ask us if this is imposing a conflict in your schedule and we will =
do our best to provide a solution.<br>
<br>
Ready to order? Please respond with a clear intent to order by submitting a=
 purchase order (PO) or written consent to proceed with this quote attached=
. Including your quote number with your purchase order is greatly appreciat=
ed.<br>
<br>
Our deposit requirements are project-specific. A 100% prepayment is require=
d for customers who do not have active payment terms with DDS. If you would=
 like to apply for terms in advance of an order please contact our orders d=
epartment at&nbsp;<a href=3D"mailto:orders@designanddirectsource.com" targe=
t=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener">orders@<wbr>designanddirectsource.com</a>.<br=
>
